_sText:
bhop_elevate

Made for legit game play. Easy - Medium difficulty bhop map with a little bit of easy climb chucked in to give it some nice game play. I was aiming for a chill vibe with some soft music to compliment the visuals.

My first time making particles so big thanks to Badges and tophatwaffle.

Thanks to everyone who tested for me.

Track list:
- LonelyDances - Pastimes (Feat. M E T A C O G)
- Montana Peltzer - Forbidden Fruit
- Spyro2 - Summer Forest (Extended)
- Fort Road - Promise of New Beginnings Among Old Endings

Enjoy!
